{"abstract":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"text":" is an abstract class that represents a shape or annotation. Shapes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"constitute the content of a map — not only the overlays atop the map, but also","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the content that forms the base map.","type":"text"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Inherits From","identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/objc(cs)NSObject"],"type":"inheritsFrom"},{"kind":"relationships","title":"Inherited By","identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNEmptyFeature","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointCollection","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeCollection"],"type":"inheritedBy"},{"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/objc(pl)NSSecureCoding"],"type":"conformsTo"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@interface","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNShape","kind":"identifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSObject","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSObject"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Create instances of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPointAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"order to use "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"’s methods. Do not create instances of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"directly, and do not create your own subclasses of this class. The shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"classes correspond to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Geometry"},{"type":"text","text":" object"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"types in the GeoJSON standard, but some have nonstandard names for backwards"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"compatibility."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Although you do not create instances of this class directly, you can use its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape\/shapeWithData:encoding:error:"},{"type":"text","text":" factory method to create one of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"concrete subclasses of "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape"},{"type":"text","text":" noted above from GeoJSON data. To access a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shape’s attributes, use the corresponding "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature"},{"type":"text","text":" class instead."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can add shapes to the map by adding them to an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Configure the appearance of an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"’s or "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shapes collectively using a concrete instance of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Alternatively, you can add some kinds of shapes directly to a map view as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"annotations or overlays."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can filter the features in a ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" or vary their layout or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"paint attributes based on the features’ geographies. Pass an ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" into an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"NSPredicate","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" with the format ","type":"text"},{"code":"SELF IN %@","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"%@ CONTAINS SELF"},{"type":"text","text":" and set the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer\/predicate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" property to that predicate, or set a layout or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"paint attribute to a similarly formatted "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSExpression"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshape"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"]]},"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Shapes","identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNEmptyFeature","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPoint","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygonFeature","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolyline","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolylineFeature","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolylineFeature","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyP